s, we can tailor our advice to organisational requirements.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Sustainability Reporting:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>we can help organisations to assess how and to what extent sustainability has been integrated into their culture, policies and practices. By working alongside colleagues within an organisation, we can combine our specialist expertise with their corporate knowledge to undertake a practical and pragmatic assessment and advise on future developments.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Sustainable Food: </strong></h3>\r\n<p>On behalf of the city of Belfast, we wrote a successful bid to be included as one of only six founder members of the UK Sustainable Food Cities programme and, subsequently, to win the first of the SFC awards. With more than 40 towns and cities now in that network, we can share our experience to help other districts establish initiatives to tackle some of the social, environmental and economic impacts of food that will help to improve the health and wellbeing of their residents.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Chairing and Facilitating: </strong></h3>\r\n<p>Drawing on long experience of leading and participating in group sessions at every scale, from small deliberative seminars to full-scale conferences, we can provide the appropriate level of input to meet your needs.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Keynote Speaker:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Jim Kitchen has spoken at conferences and other events, frequently and widely, on many aspects of sustainability, from transport to wildlife trade, from climate to conservation, from food to fisheries. He can tailor his presentations for a wide range of audiences.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" full_screen_row_position=\"middle\" bg_color=\"#333333\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"light\" text_align=\"left\" top_padding=\"8%\" bottom_padding=\"8%\" color_overlay=\"#2ecc71\" overlay_strength=\"1\" shape_divider_position=\"top\" shape_divider_height=\"250\" shape_type=\"tilt_alt\"][vc_co