stainable Development Goals are a common blueprint for a sustainable future; they are relevant to developed nations as well as developing countries; they are applicable to communities, to households and individuals, as well as to governments, businesses and the voluntary sector.\r\n\r\nYou can find out much more about the Sustainable Development Goals <a href=\"https://sustainabledevelopment.un.org/sdgs\">here</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"in_container\" full_screen_row_position=\"middle\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" bottom_padding=\"8%\" overlay_strength=\"0.3\" shape_divider_position=\"bottom\" shape_type=\"\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" width=\"1/1\" tablet_text_alignment=\"default\" phone_text_alignment=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\"][image_with_animation image_url=\"5902\" alignment=\"center\" animation=\"Fade In\" border_radius=\"none\" box_shadow=\"none\" max_width=\"100%\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" full_screen_row_position=\"middle\" bg_color=\"#333333\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"light\" text_align=\"left\" top_padding=\"9%\" bottom_padding=\"8%\" color_overlay=\"#2ecc71\" overlay_strength=\"1\" shape_divider_position=\"top\" shape_divider_height=\"250\" shape_type=\"waves_opacity_alt\"][vc_column centered_text=\"true\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" width=\"1/6\" tablet_text_alignment=\"default\" phone_text_alignment=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\"][/vc_column][vc_column centered_text=\"true\" column_padding=\"no-e